/// Context Routes
///
/// GET /v1/packages/{name}/{version}/context — Get Forge context file
///
/// Handler defined in main.fg:
///   handle_get_context() — Reads data/packages/{name}/versions/{version}/context.fg
///
/// The context file is the API surface of a package version — the .fg source
/// that consumers use to understand what the package exports (extern fns,
/// component templates, types, etc.)
///
/// Response: {"package": "...", "version": "...", "context": "<file contents>"}
